<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 16:10:13 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>当这些以色列士兵在加沙死亡时，他们的同性恋身份也随之消失</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/when-these-israeli-soldiers-died-in-gaza-their-gay-identity-died-with-them/0000018f-9fc1-da35-a3af-dfeb78f20000</link><description>“诺姆的家人只是想埋葬一切，隐藏他的身份和身份”：他们的同性恋伴侣在加沙的死亡意味着这些失去亲人的伴侣必须独自应对这一损失，没有周围人或国家的支持</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 15:15:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/when-these-israeli-soldiers-died-in-gaza-their-gay-identity-died-with-them/0000018f-9fc1-da35-a3af-dfeb78f20000</guid></item><item><title>我父亲是加沙的人质。巴勒斯坦人不是我的敌人——盲目的仇恨才是</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/my-father-is-a-hostage-in-gaza-palestinians-are-not-my-enemy/0000018f-a4a7-dca3-a7cf-a5b721d30000</link><description>当我们流血和悲伤时，对于像我自己这样的家庭来说，我们对亲人的命运悬在希望和绝望之间，有时我想大喊，极左派对以色列的沾沾自喜的仇恨是徒劳的。我们迫切需要的是他们对为正义与和平而努力的以色列人和巴勒斯坦人的支持</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 14:44:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/my-father-is-a-hostage-in-gaza-palestinians-are-not-my-enemy/0000018f-a4a7-dca3-a7cf-a5b721d30000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡否认以色列军队在10月7日之前警告他哈马斯打算袭击以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-denies-the-idf-warned-him-before-oct-7-of-hamas-intention-to-attack-israel/0000018f-a5b0-d0b4-a3cf-b7bc32b10000</link><description>以色列国防军周四证实，在加沙战争爆发之前，它曾警告总理内塔尼亚胡，司法改革引发的危机正在鼓励伊朗、真主党和哈马斯冒对以色列采取潜在行动的风险</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 14:30:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-denies-the-idf-warned-him-before-oct-7-of-hamas-intention-to-attack-israel/0000018f-a5b0-d0b4-a3cf-b7bc32b10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列妇女试图将山羊偷偷带进圣殿山献祭，导致山羊死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/goat-dies-as-israeli-woman-attempts-to-sneak-it-into-temple-mount-for-sacrifice/0000018f-a54f-d8a2-a3cf-a5cfbedf0000</link><description>当这只山羊开始在耶路撒冷老城入口处的女子衣服下走动并发出噪音时，警方接到了警报。在极右翼部长伊塔马尔·本-格维尔的支持下，走私动物献祭的企图有所增加</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 14:20:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/goat-dies-as-israeli-woman-attempts-to-sneak-it-into-temple-mount-for-sacrifice/0000018f-a54f-d8a2-a3cf-a5cfbedf0000</guid></item><item><title>黄金耶路撒冷：这是以色列首都出售的最昂贵的公寓</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/business/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/jerusalem-of-gold-luxury-penthouse-sets-new-price-record-in-israels-capital/0000018f-a4f1-d8a2-a3cf-a4f3bd850000</link><description>该住宅以 1700 万美元的价格出售给计划移民的非以色列人，每平方米的价格为 30,750 美元。它毗邻一座建于 20 世纪 50 年代的历史豪宅</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 13:18:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/business/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/jerusalem-of-gold-luxury-penthouse-sets-new-price-record-in-israels-capital/0000018f-a4f1-d8a2-a3cf-a4f3bd850000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方起诉两名极右翼抗议者袭击失去亲人的父亲</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-indict-two-far-right-protesters-for-assault-of-bereaved-israeli-father/0000018f-a4d5-dca3-a7cf-a5f5160c0000</link><description>加迪·凯德姆 (Gadi Kedem) 在哈马斯 10 月 7 日的袭击中失去了六名家人，他在特拉维夫的一次集会上抗议释放加沙的人质时遭到袭击。据称，一名袭击者大喊“你的孩子被杀了，真好，左派！”凯德姆的妻子</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 12:45:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-indict-two-far-right-protesters-for-assault-of-bereaved-israeli-father/0000018f-a4d5-dca3-a7cf-a5f5160c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军调查发现以色列军队违反规定，误杀拉法的联合国援助人员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/idf-probe-israeli-forces-breached-regulations-mistakenly-killed-un-aid-worker-in-gaza/0000018f-a50e-db21-a9ff-b53eaf700000</link><description>以色列国防军上周对一名联合国工作人员死亡事件进行的调查发现，他的车辆在没有以色列国防军协调的情况下行驶在禁行道路上。尽管标有联合国字母 - 并且违反了有关人道主义工作者的规定 - 该车辆首先遭到炮弹袭击，然后在附近遭到手榴弹袭击</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 12:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/idf-probe-israeli-forces-breached-regulations-mistakenly-killed-un-aid-worker-in-gaza/0000018f-a50e-db21-a9ff-b53eaf700000</guid></item><item><title>以色列为期两天的约旦河西岸行动造成12名巴勒斯坦人死亡、25人受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/12-palestinians-killed-25-wounded-in-israels-two-day-jenin-operation/0000018f-a536-df13-a3af-b536d3a80000</link><description>军方周二在杰宁市和邻近的城市难民营发起了这次行动，作为镇压该地区武装分子的一部分。巴勒斯坦伊斯兰圣战武装组织表示，其战士与以色列军队作战</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 11:48:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/12-palestinians-killed-25-wounded-in-israels-two-day-jenin-operation/0000018f-a536-df13-a3af-b536d3a80000</guid></item><item><title>谁害怕承认巴勒斯坦国？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/whos-afraid-of-recognizing-a-palestinian-state/0000018f-a496-d8a2-a3cf-a49735d50000</link><description>即使巴勒斯坦国是一个正在形成的“失败国家”，它仍然是以色列必须考虑的问题。你不能通过完全否定辩论和进程来塑造和影响辩论和进程，就像本杰明·内塔尼亚胡试图做的那样</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 11:09:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/whos-afraid-of-recognizing-a-palestinian-state/0000018f-a496-d8a2-a3cf-a49735d50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列内盖夫沙漠教堂发现早期基督教船只涂鸦</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-05-23/ty-article/early-christian-ship-graffiti-found-at-church-in-israels-negev-desert/0000018f-a4ce-d639-a5bf-f7fe1d940000</link><description>在南部城市拉哈特的一个新社区的建设工作中，考古学家发现了六世纪的教堂，上面有可能将朝圣者带到圣地的船只的照片</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 10:34:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-05-23/ty-article/early-christian-ship-graffiti-found-at-church-in-israels-negev-desert/0000018f-a4ce-d639-a5bf-f7fe1d940000</guid></item><item><title>崩溃还是认可？巴勒斯坦领导人面临关键时刻</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/on-verge-of-collapse-and-recognition-the-palestinian-leadership-faces-a-moment-of-truth/0000018f-a482-db21-a9ff-b4bec6b90000</link><description>欧洲国家承认巴勒斯坦国主要是对加沙局势的回应。但如果西岸的巴勒斯坦领导层不寻求变革，即使获得更多国家的承认也不会改变当地的局势</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 10:27:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/on-verge-of-collapse-and-recognition-the-palestinian-leadership-faces-a-moment-of-truth/0000018f-a482-db21-a9ff-b4bec6b90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列同意对在以色列拘留期间死亡的加沙医生进行尸检</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-agrees-to-perform-autopsy-on-gazan-doctor-who-died-in-israeli-custody/0000018f-a494-dca3-a7cf-a5b542f40000</link><description>Adnan Al-Bursh 医生现年 53 岁，是六个孩子的父亲，也是加沙市 Al-Shifa 医院骨科主任。他的妻子亚斯明向以色列人权医生协会的代表提交了尸检请求</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 09:30:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-agrees-to-perform-autopsy-on-gazan-doctor-who-died-in-israeli-custody/0000018f-a494-dca3-a7cf-a5b542f40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列官员担心国际法院将裁定停止加沙战斗，准备实施制裁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/icj-to-rule-on-friday-on-measures-over-israels-military-offensive-in-rafah-gaza-strip/0000018f-a499-d639-a5bf-f7f90c950000</link><description>以色列官员担心，此前并未命令以色列停止加沙战争的国际法院可能会对以色列的军事进攻采取更强硬的立场，从而可能使其面临国际制裁</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 08:42:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/icj-to-rule-on-friday-on-measures-over-israels-military-offensive-in-rafah-gaza-strip/0000018f-a499-d639-a5bf-f7f90c950000</guid></item><item><title>被俘女兵的视频揭露了以色列10月7日最可怕的失败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/video-of-captive-female-soldiers-exposes-the-most-horrific-failing-of-october-7/0000018f-a201-d5dc-a7df-eee7f4a50000</link><description>视频中最明显的事情之一是哈马斯绑架者的冷漠，他们似乎拥有所有的时间。那些对失败负责的人不能继续掌权太久</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 03:00:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/video-of-captive-female-soldiers-exposes-the-most-horrific-failing-of-october-7/0000018f-a201-d5dc-a7df-eee7f4a50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军称有 30 枚火箭弹袭击以色列北部地区；以色列无人机在黎巴嫩杀死真主党官员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article-live/hamas-video-of-captive-idf-spotters-was-manipulated-female-soldiers-treated-ethically/0000018f-a31d-d476-a7df-e37d05110000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡：安全机构没有警告哈马斯从加沙发动袭击，事实恰恰相反 ■ 以色列就巴勒斯坦举动谴责爱尔兰、挪威、西班牙特使 ■ 欧盟外交政策负责人：所有欧盟捐助者恢复近东救济工程处资助 ■ 匈牙利不会拘留以色列内塔尼亚胡国际刑事法院裁决 ■ 以色列战时内阁指示谈判小组重启人质交易谈判</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 01:50:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article-live/hamas-video-of-captive-idf-spotters-was-manipulated-female-soldiers-treated-ethically/0000018f-a31d-d476-a7df-e37d05110000</guid></item><item><title>被俘虏的以色列国防军观察员的视频更加证明了内塔尼亚胡的失败。他必须走了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/video-of-captive-idf-spotters-is-more-proof-of-netanyahus-failure-he-has-to-go/0000018f-a282-d8ed-a19f-bec210410000</link><description>以色列总理继续用“全面胜利”的口号席卷公众，而视频中显示的以色列女兵仍被关押在加沙。他们的目光应该萦绕在他醒着的每一个时刻</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 23:02:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/.premium/video-of-captive-idf-spotters-is-more-proof-of-netanyahus-failure-he-has-to-go/0000018f-a282-d8ed-a19f-bec210410000</guid></item><item><title>尼基·黑利 (Nikki Haley) 抨击拜登因以色列暂停武器而“愚蠢”，并表示将在 11 月投票给特朗普</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/nikki-haley-slams-foolish-biden-over-israel-arms-pause-says-will-vote-trump-in-november/0000018f-a234-d8a2-a3cf-a6b7ad7b0000</link><description>美国前驻联合国大使、特朗普2024年初选最主要对手的背书，对拜登竞选来说是一个打击</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 21:33:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-23/ty-article/nikki-haley-slams-foolish-biden-over-israel-arms-pause-says-will-vote-trump-in-november/0000018f-a234-d8a2-a3cf-a6b7ad7b0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦人报告以色列军队在约旦河西岸杰宁袭击中造成 11 人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/palestinians-report-10-killed-by-israeli-forces-in-raid-on-west-banks-jenin/0000018f-a08a-d35f-a1df-ffcbd2620000</link><description>一名巴勒斯坦妇女在乘坐的军车碾压爆炸装置时受重伤；自以色列军队周二开始行动以来，拉马拉卫生部表示已有 25 名巴勒斯坦人受伤</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 18:48:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-22/ty-article/palestinians-report-10-killed-by-israeli-forces-in-raid-on-west-banks-jenin/0000018f-a08a-d35f-a1df-ffcbd2620000</guid></item><item><title>面对女性人质的残酷镜头，以色列政府以无耻的傲慢回应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-22/ty-article/.highlight/israeli-government-responds-to-brutal-film-of-women-hostages-with-shameless-arrogance/0000018f-a0cf-d639-a5bf-f3ffef930000</link><description>10月7日被绑架的五名年轻女兵的家人发布了一段被绑架的视频，希望唤起人们的羞耻感，以此作为唤起内塔尼亚胡政府良知的“最后手段”。至少一位利库德集团高级领导人显然没有这种耻辱</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 18:32:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-22/ty-article/.highlight/israeli-government-responds-to-brutal-film-of-women-hostages-with-shameless-arrogance/0000018f-a0cf-d639-a5bf-f3ffef930000</guid></item><item><